<p>Very nice spin up the canyon today, despite the hot, desiccating breeze.  Lots of folks out on the road, which is great to see.  Since I saw no one else out there, how did your lunches go?</p>
<h6>Upcoming Events</h6>
<p>Tomorrow is <em>Bike to Work Day</em>.  Apparently CU is giving away limited edition <em>BtWD</em> tee-shirts at their UMC and Math stations, so get there early.  Should be some good food too.  If you haven't already, <a href="http://www.drcog.org/btwd2008/dsp_registerIndividual.cfm">sign up</a> now!</p>
<p>This morning, I went down to the county office and completed my <em>Adopt-A-Road</em> safety training.  So, we're good to go for July 10: Frenzy Rubbish Day!</p>
